cat << EOF
Provides an interface to easily send hidden
files or any arbitrary data to
HTTP clients.  HTTP_Download can gain its data
from variables, files or
stream resources.
It features:
- Basic caching capabilities
- Basic throttling mechanism
- On-the-fly gzip-compression
- Ranges (partial downloads and resuming)
- Delivery of on-the-fly generated archives
through Archive_Tar and Archive_Zip
- Sending of PgSQL LOBs without the need to
read all data in prior to sending
EOF

source  $SECTION_DIRECTORY/PEAR_DETAILS
